9 An Act related to education; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 13-101.2, as last amended by Section 1,
10 Chapter 246, O.S.L. 2025 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
13-101.2), which relates to the Lindsey Nicole Henry
11 Scholarships for Students with Disabilities Program;
requiring school districts to make an eligibility
12 decision for special education services within sixty
days of receiving parental request; determining
13 student eligibility when the sixty-day timeline is
not met; providing maximum scholarship calculations
14 for certain eligible students; requiring supplement
of scholarship award after certain determination;
15 providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
